          "service_name": "Road Freight",
          "service_card_description": "Reliable road transportation for cargo across UAE with flexible pickup and delivery options.",
          "service_more_details": "<p>Our road freight service provides safe and efficient transportation across the UAE. With a modern fleet and experienced drivers, we ensure your cargo is delivered on time and handled with care. This service is ideal for local shipments, warehouse transfers, and scheduled deliveries between cities. We offer flexible pickup times, secure handling, and real-time coordination to make road transportation smooth and reliable.</p>\n"
