          "service_name": "Sea Freight",
          "service_card_description": "Affordable sea cargo solutions for large shipments, furniture, vehicles, and commercial goods.",
          "service_more_details": "<p>Sea freight is the most cost-effective way to transport large or heavy shipments internationally. Our sea cargo service handles everything from packaging and container loading to customs clearance and shipping. Whether you are sending personal items, business goods, or bulk cargo from the UAE to Sri Lanka, we ensure secure handling and efficient delivery. We offer both full container load (FCL) and less-than-container load (LCL) options depending on your shipping needs.</p>\n"
