          "service_name": "Door to Door Delivery",
          "service_card_description": "Complete logistics service from your location in Dubai to your doorstep in Sri Lanka",
          "service_more_details": "<p>Our door to door delivery service provides a hassle-free shipping experience. We handle the entire logistics process including pickup, packaging, documentation, shipping, customs clearance, and final delivery. This service is perfect for customers who want a simple and convenient solution without managing multiple shipping steps. From your home or office in Dubai to your doorstep in Sri Lanka, we ensure a smooth and reliable delivery process.</p>\n"
