          "service_name": "Cargo Packing & Handling",
          "service_card_description": "Professional packing and secure handling to protect your cargo during international shipping.",
          "service_more_details": "<p>Our cargo packing and handling service ensures that your items are properly packed and protected for safe transportation. We use high-quality packing materials and professional techniques to secure fragile goods, furniture, electronics, and commercial products. Our experienced team carefully prepares cargo to prevent damage during loading, shipping, and unloading. This service is ideal for customers who want extra safety and reliability when sending goods from the UAE to Sri Lanka.</p>\n"
